FBIS4-35987 "drnes108_o_94007" FBIS-NES-94-108 Daily Report 4 Jun 1994 SYRIA Iranian Foreign Minister Meets al-Asad, al-Shar' Iranian Foreign Minister Meets al-Asad, al-Shar' Discusses Israeli `Escalation' JN0406154094 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1515 GMT 4 Jun 94 JN0406154094 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] At 1230 today, President Hafiz al-Asad received Iranian Foreign Minister Dr. 'Ali Akbar Velayati and the delegation accompanying him. Foreign Minister Faruq al-Shar' and the Iranian ambassador in Damascus attended. Dr. Velayati conveyed to the president a message from Iranian President Hashemi-Rafsanjani concerning developments in the region. The president asked Velayati to convey a reply message. Discussion during the meeting revolved around a number of issues concerning the situation in the region and Israel's escalation of tension in it, as well as issues of mutual concern.
